👉 Follow @bodysmartfitness for the best mindset, nutrition and fitness tips Follow 👉 @bodysmartfitness  
 
"Your inner monologue is the most important thing in your life. " says Jaymie Moran from @bodysmartfitness  
   
Whatever you tell yourself, good or bad, you will probably become.   
   
💪 "Whatever the mind believes the body achieves" is a good quote here.   
   
😞 If you think you're worthless and stupid, you'll act worthless and stupid.   
   
😄 If you think you are strong and resilient, you'll act strong and resilient.   
   
🧠 @bodysmartfitness go into this in great depth with their clients and get them to understand that their identity has been entirely created by their own thoughts.   
   
If you think you're unfit and lazy 👉 you'll act unfit and lazy.   
If you think you're always too busy to take action 👉 you'll be too busy to take action.   
If you think you are weak and lack willpower 👉 you will act weak without willpower.   
   
💪 So try changing your personal beliefs to change your identity and change your daily actions and habits.
